11 May






Events



           10:00 am
        


        Information Session: Cash and Check Deposit Enhancements
      




Information Session: Cash and Check Deposit Enhancements

        10:00am, Thursday May 11
      



The Office of the Treasurer is hosting an info session to help department depositors understand the changes to the cash and check deposit process, including the new J.P. Morgan mobile app.
Topics include an overview of the cash and check project, deposit methods and best practices, a walk through of mobile deposit tools, and a Q&A session. 
Join us from 10-11 a.m. on Thursday, May 11. Register now. 
To stay up to date on the changes, please visit the Cash and Check Deposit Enhancements news page.
